The idea of making frequent phone calls to stay in touch with friends or acquaintances doesn't resonate with my personality type, and I may feel drained or overwhelmed by the constant need to communicate in this way.

7 - Strongly Disagree

This can make it difficult for me to fully appreciate or enjoy the positive attention, as I'm constantly worrying about how I'll let others down.
